title: Juul Respen
text:
Juul Respen (born 17 October 1998) is a Dutch <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who plays for <a href="RKVV%20EVV">EVV</a>.
Club career.
He made his professional debut in the <a href="Eerste%20Divisie">Eerste Divisie</a> for <a href="VVV-Venlo">VVV-Venlo</a> on 4 November 2016 in a game against <a href="FC%20Dordrecht">FC Dordrecht</a>.
